doc.after: Since 1788 the basis of Australian culture has been strongly influenced by Anglo Celtic Western culture 291 292 Distinctive cultural features have also arisen from Australia s natural environment and Indigenous cultures 293 294 Since the mid 20th century American popular culture has strongly influenced Australia particularly through television and cinema 295 Other cultural influences come from neighbouring Asian countries and through large scale immigration from non English speaking nations 295 296
